<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Casa do Açaí | O Melhor de Taubaté</title>
    <style>
        /* ==========================================================================
           CONFIGURAÇÕES GERAIS E PALETA DE CORES
           ========================================================================== */
        :root {
            --purple-main: #6A1B9A;
            --purple-dark: #4A148C;
            --purple-light: #F3E5F5;
            --purple-bg: #FAF5FF;
            --lime-accent: #AEEA00;
            --lime-hover: #9BE000;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --dark-text: #1A052E;
            --light-text: #614E75;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(74, 20, 140, 0.08);
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--dark-text);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Container padrão */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* Títulos Globais */
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--light-text);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 48px auto;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* Botões */
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-whatsapp {
            background-color: var(--lime-accent);
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 234, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-whatsapp:hover {
            background-color: var(--lime-hover);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(174, 234, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--white);
            border: 2px solid var(--white);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .btn-purple {
            background-color: var(--purple-main);
            color: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(106, 27, 154, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-purple:hover {
            background-color: var(--purple-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(74, 20, 140, 0.3);
        }

        /* Botão Flutuante do WhatsApp */
        .float-whatsapp {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            background-color: #25D366;
            color: white;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            z-index: 999;
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .float-whatsapp:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(10deg);
            background-color: #128C7E;
        }

        .float-whatsapp svg {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            fill: white;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           HEADER / NAVBAR
           ========================================================================== */
        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 80px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--purple-main);
        }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            list-style: none;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--dark-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--purple-main);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           HERO SECTION
           ========================================================================== */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-dark) 0%, var(--purple-main) 100%);
            padding: 160px 0 100px 0;
            color: var(--white);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://i.postimg.cc/63V1gsYb/image.png') center/cover no-repeat;
            opacity: 0.08;
            mix-blend-mode: overlay;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
            gap: 48px;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            line-height: 1.15;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
            max-width: 540px;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-image-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-image-container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 380px;
            height: 380px;
            background: rgba(174, 234, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(40px);
            z-index: 1;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .hero-img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            z-index: 2;
            transform: rotate(-2deg);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .hero-img:hover {
            transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.02);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           SOBRE NÓS
           ========================================================================== */
        .about {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .about-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--light-text);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           DIFERENCIAIS
           ========================================================================== */
        .features {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--purple-bg);
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid rgba(106, 27, 154, 0.03);
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(74, 20, 140, 0.12);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            background-color: var(--purple-light);
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .feature-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .feature-info p {
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           CARDÁPIO DE DESTAQUE
           ========================================================================== */
        .menu-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .menu-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .menu-img-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            height: 220px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #eee;
        }

        .menu-card-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .menu-card:hover .menu-card-img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }

        .menu-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            background-color: var(--purple-dark);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .menu-info {
            padding: 24px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .menu-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .menu-info p {
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .menu-action {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding-top: 16px;
        }

        .menu-tag {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--purple-main);
            background-color: var(--purple-light);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .menu-btn-order {
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .menu-btn-order:hover {
            color: var(--purple-main);
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           DEPOIMENTOS (PROVA SOCIAL)
           ========================================================================== */
        .testimonials {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--purple-bg);
        }

        .testimonials-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
        }

        .stars {
            color: #FFC107;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .user-avatar {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--purple-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
        }

        .user-details h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .user-details span {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #9b8ba3;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           CALL TO ACTION (CTA)
           ========================================================================== */
        .cta-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-main) 0%, var(--purple-dark) 100%);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .cta-container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           LOCALIZAÇÃO
           ========================================================================== */
        .location {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .location-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: 48px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .location-info h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .location-info p {
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .location-details-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .location-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .location-icon {
            color: var(--purple-main);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .location-text h4 {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--purple-dark);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .location-text p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .map-container {
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            height: 400px;
            border: 4px solid var(--purple-light);
        }

        .map-container iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           FOOTER (RODAPÉ)
           ========================================================================== */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--dark-text);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            padding: 60px 0 30px 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.5fr repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .footer-brand h3 {
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer-brand p {
            max-width: 320px;
        }

        .footer-links h4, .footer-contact h4 {
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .footer-links ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--lime-accent);
            padding-left: 4px;
        }

        .footer-contact p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            background-color: var(--purple-main);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           RESPONSIVIDADE (MEDIA QUERIES)
           ========================================================================== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 40px;
            }
            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
            .hero-content p {
                margin: 0 auto 32px auto;
            }
            .hero-buttons {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .about-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }
            .about-image-wrapper {
                order: 2;
            }
            .location-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .nav-menu {
                display: none; /* Em produção adicionaria menu hamburguer */
            }
            .footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            .cta-section h2 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <script>
        const CONFIG_CASA_ACAI = {
            whatsapp_number: "5512999999999", // Altere para o número real com DDD de Taubaté
            msg_geral: "Olá! Vi o site e gostaria de fazer um pedido de açaí.",
            msg_tradicional: "Olá! Gostaria de pedir o Açaí Tradicional do site.",
            msg_frutas: "Olá! Gostaria de pedir o Açaí com Frutas do site.",
            msg_premium: "Olá! Gostaria de pedir o Açaí Premium do site.",
            msg_combos: "Olá! Gostaria de conhecer as Combinações Especiais da casa."
        };

        function getWhatsLink(type) {
            let base = `https://wa.me/${CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.whatsapp_number}?text=`;
            if(type === 'tradicional') return base + encodeURIComponent(CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.msg_tradicional);
            if(type === 'frutas') return base + encodeURIComponent(CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.msg_frutas);
            if(type === 'premium') return base + encodeURIComponent(CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.msg_premium);
            if(type === 'combos') return base + encodeURIComponent(CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.msg_combos);
            return base + encodeURIComponent(CONFIG_CASA_ACAI.msg_geral);
        }

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            // Vincula dinamicamente os links corretos aos botões do WhatsApp
            document.querySelectorAll(".link-wa-dinamico").forEach(btn => {
                let target = btn.getAttribute("data-target") || 'geral';
                btn.setAttribute("href", getWhatsLink(target));
                btn.setAttribute("target", "_blank");
            });
        });
    </script>

    <a class="float-whatsapp link-wa-dinamico" data-target="geral" aria-label="Chamar no WhatsApp">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32">
            <path d="M16 2a14 14 0 0 0-12.08 21.06L2 29l6.14-1.61A14 14 0 1 0 16 2zm7.62 19.82c-.32.91-1.6 1.77-2.61 1.92-.69.1-1.58.13-2.55-.2a13.3 13.3 0 0 1-5.69-3.55 11.23 11.23 0 0 1-2.45-4.22 5.61 5.61 0 0 1 .4-4.52c.26-.35.58-.72.88-1.07.32-.35.42-.58.61-.93.19-.38.1-.7-.03-1s-1.15-2.79-1.57-3.81c-.42-1-.83-1-1.15-1h-1a1.92 1.92 0 0 0-1.41.64c-.48.55-1.86 1.83-1.86 4.45s1.9 5.16 2.16 5.52 3.65 5.61 8.93 7.82c1.26.52 2.24.84 3 .1a5.06 5.06 0 0 0 1.5-1c.42-.42.54-.93.8-1.41a1.27 1.27 0 0 0-.07-1.31c-.13-.26-.54-.54-1.12-.83s-3.4-1.67-3.92-1.86-.92-.29-1.31.29-.1.67-1.5 2.24c-.16.19-.32.22-.51.13a11.13 11.13 0 0 1-3.77-2.33 12.3 12.3 0 0 1-2.61-3.26c-.19-.32 0-.48.09-.61s.42-.48.61-.71a3.15 3.15 0 0 0 .41-.58 1 1 0 0 0-.05-1c-.06-.16-.54-1.31-.74-1.83z"/>
        </svg>
    </a>

    <header>
        <div class="container nav-container">
            <a href="#" class="logo">🍇 Casa do <span>Açaí</span></a>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="#inicio" class="nav-link">Início</a></li>
                <li><a href="#sobre" class="nav-link">Sobre Nós</a></li>
                <li><a href="#diferenciais" class="nav-link">Diferenciais</a></li>
                <li><a href="#cardapio" class="nav-link">Cardápio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#depoimentos" class="nav-link">Depoimentos</a></li>
                <li><a href="#localizacao" class="nav-link">Onde Estamos</a></li>
                <li><a href="#cardapio" class="btn btn-purple" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Ver Cardápio</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="inicio">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>O Melhor Açaí do Parque Santa Terezinha em Taubaté!</h1>
                <p>Cremoso, geladinho e preparado com ingredientes selecionados para deixar seu dia muito mais saboroso.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a class="btn btn-whatsapp link-wa-dinamico" data-target="geral">💬 Pedir pelo WhatsApp</a>
                    <a href="#cardapio" class="btn btn-outline">📋 Ver Cardápio</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-container">
                <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/63V1gsYb/image.png" alt="Taça de Açaí Premium Completa" class="hero-img">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

